00:40:33.679 --> 00:40:35.840
He said, "The magic is
over."

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:36.909
What was the magic?
 

00:40:36.909 --> 00:40:40.860
It was what this country
represents to Europeans.

00:40:40.860 --> 00:40:43.199
The magic is over.
 

00:40:43.199 --> 00:40:45.614
Then he paused and he said,
"Things will never be the

00:40:45.614 --> 00:40:46.420
same again."
 

00:40:46.420 --> 00:40:54.581
So, I guess just in conclusion,
it's up to you to believe in

00:40:54.581 --> 00:40:57.960
human rights and believe in the
value of people,

00:40:57.960 --> 00:41:01.670
whether they're clandestine,
or legal immigrants or not,

00:41:01.670 --> 00:41:04.833
and that human rights should be
written on the face of this

00:41:04.833 --> 00:41:07.920
country as well,
and that you can return and

00:41:07.920 --> 00:41:09.440
restore that magic.
 

